Aural translation
by Hektor6766 » Wed 10.06.2010 3:36 pm I've been watching some old anime to improve my listening skill, and there's a line from Maisson Ikkoku I wanted to check. It wasn't subtitled, so I had to translate straight from the audio. Here's a link:http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R5ASUK7ZDuU It's at 3:16八神息吹 (I love that name!) Looks out her window at the night sky, clasps her hands together and says, 「今度こそ……この真実な愛を貫いて得も制定わ。」"This time...I will break through to attain this true love."At least I think that's what she says.
