Re: Aural translation
by Hyperworm » Thu 10.07.2010 8:31 am "'go' through" doesn't feel right here...This is 貫く as in 「正義を貫く(enforce ~)」「自分の主義を貫く(stick with ~ all the way through, see ~ through)」 etc, isn't it?"This time, I'm definitely going to make this true love work"?"This time, I'm definitely not going to let this true love fail"?
